{
  "enabled": true,
  "version": "1",
  "name": "analyze-context-usage",
  "description": "分析主 Agent 上下文使用情况",
  "when": {
    "type": "userTriggered"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Please analyze context usage:\n\n**Instructions**:\n1. Use context-gatherer subagent to read all markdown files in .kiro/docs/ directory\n2. Analyze the summaries returned by context-gatherer to count total lines\n3. Estimate token usage for Steering documents based on summaries\n4. Compare with v2.0.6 architecture improvements (88% reduction)\n5. Identify opportunities for further optimization\n6. Suggest which documents could be split or summarized\n\n**Follow KIRO-RULES.md**: Never directly use readFile or readMultipleFiles. Always use context-gatherer subagent for reading project documentation.\n\nProvide a detailed context usage report."
  }
}
